# Commit Message Convention
# Format: type(scope): description
#
# Types:
# feat:     New feature
# fix:      Bug fix
# docs:     Documentation changes
# style:    Formatting, missing semi-colons, etc.
# refactor: Code restructuring
# test:     Adding tests
# chore:    Maintenance tasks
#
# Examples:
# feat(auth): implement JWT refresh token rotation
# fix(attendance): resolve race condition in bulk save
# docs(api): update Swagger documentation for grade endpoints
#
# Scope should be a feature area or component name
# Description should be imperative, lower case, no period